About ISAL

Mission
The International Society for Artificial Life (ISAL) is a democratic, international, professional society dedicated to 
promoting research and education in Artificial Life. 

Our mission is to 
1) create a supportive and inclusive community focused on ethical and effective scholarship in Artificial Life and 
2) increase the external impact, accessibility, and relevance of scholarship in Artificial Life. 

The vision of the International Society for Artificial Life is for the field of Artificial Life to be widely known 
and valued as a highly interdisciplinary, impactful, and welcoming area of scholarship.


